---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
---

<Layout title="Features">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Features</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc"></Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-8">
      
      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Conversational AI
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Recognify’s core feature is centered around <strong>conversational artificial intelligence</strong>. This AI provides users with <strong>emotional support, reflective conversations, insights, and understanding</strong>. Unlike simple chatbots, Recognify’s AI is designed using <strong>cognitive psychological models</strong> that mimic human mental processes during conversations.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Most mental health and self-improvement AIs are limited to <strong>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT)</strong>, failing to account for individual uniqueness. Recognify’s AI <strong>tailors its approach</strong> to each person's unique qualities, desires, and burdens—adapting much like a life coach or therapist.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        The Greatness Garden
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Recognify is the world’s first self-improvement platform that acknowledges the <strong>complexity of personal growth</strong>. Many digital solutions fail because they do not provide <strong>engagement, accountability, or continued motivation</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Recognify’s <strong>Greatness Garden</strong> is an interactive <strong>virtual garden</strong> that visually symbolizes personal progress. As users advance toward their goals, their garden <strong>flourishes</strong>, creating a motivating and rewarding experience.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Personalized Exercises
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Achieving dreams isn’t easy, and self-improvement requires <strong>active effort</strong>. Recognify provides <strong>scientifically validated mental exercises</strong> that function like <strong>workouts for the brain</strong>—helping users reshape negative thoughts, reduce self-doubt, and build resilience.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Unlike generic CBT assignments, Recognify <strong>personalizes these exercises</strong> based on each user’s goals, values, and challenges. This ensures that the exercises are <strong>relevant, effective, and engaging</strong> rather than just another task.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Reflection and Journaling
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Reflection is an <strong>essential skill for growth</strong>, yet few people utilize it effectively. Recognify supports <strong>guided reflective cycles and journaling</strong>—two research-backed techniques that enhance <strong>well-being, career success, and relationships</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Many people get trapped in <strong>unproductive rumination</strong> or fail to gain meaningful insights from experiences. Recognify ensures that reflection is <strong>structured, productive, and enjoyable</strong>, helping users step toward their dreams, one reflection at a time.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-bold text-3xl text-gray-800">
        Privacy and Security
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        Recognify is committed to <strong>user privacy and data security</strong>, following the highest standards, including <strong>GDPR compliance</strong>. Unlike many tech companies, Recognify <strong>does not sell or share user data</strong> with third parties or governments.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-500">
        All conversations and actions are <strong>fully anonymized</strong> to protect users from data leaks or hacks. Additionally, Recognify only uses data for research purposes with <strong>explicit user consent</strong> and provides an easy way for users to request data deletion.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
